one recognizes the transpose of the matrix formula_123 considered above, and its determinant (as element of is also &quot;p&quot;(&quot;φ&quot;). To derive from this equation that , one left-multiplies by the adjugate matrix of formula_131, which is defined in the matrix ring , giving
